| ID | Requirement | Target |
|----|-------------|--------|
| NFR-I18N-01 | Bilingual UI: Bulgarian (default) and English | Required |
| NFR-I18N-02 | All UI strings use `next-intl` translations; no hardcoded display strings | Required |
| NFR-I18N-03 | BG/EN message files must have identical key sets | Required (enforced by CI) |
| NFR-I18N-04 | AI outputs generated in user's preferred language | Required |
| NFR-I18N-05 | Source documents processed in BG, EN, DE, FR, RO | Required |
| NFR-WCAG-01 | WCAG 2.1 AA accessibility compliance | Required |

### 10.7 Observability

| ID | Requirement | Target |
|----|-------------|--------|
| NFR-OBS-01 | Prometheus `/metrics` endpoint on each service | Required |
| NFR-OBS-02 | Structured JSON logging via `structlog` in production | Required |
| NFR-OBS-03 | `x-request-id` correlation header on all API requests | Required |
| NFR-OBS-04 | KraftData eval runs for continuous AI agent quality monitoring | Required |
| NFR-OBS-05 | Admin introspection endpoints: circuit breaker state, rate limit state, execution queue state | Required |

### 10.8 Maintainability & Testing

| ID | Requirement | Target |
|----|-------------|--------|
| NFR-TEST-01 | Minimum 80% automated test coverage across all services | Required |
| NFR-TEST-02 | ATDD-first: failing acceptance tests written before implementation | Required |
| NFR-TEST-03 | testcontainers + respx for all backend integration tests | Required |
| NFR-TEST-04 | Playwright E2E specs for all frontend ACs before story marked done | Required |
| NFR-TEST-05 | Per-test transaction rollback for DB isolation; Redis flush for cache isolation | Required |
| NFR-TEST-06 | Cross-tenant negative test for every company-scoped endpoint | Required |

