## 14. Milestones & Phasing

| Phase | Epics | Sprint | Key Delivery |
|-------|-------|--------|--------------|
| **Phase 1: Foundation** | E01 (Infra), E02 (Auth), E03 (Frontend Shell) | 1–2 | Running services; user can register and log in |
| **Phase 2: Data & AI** | E04 (AI Gateway), E05 (Data Pipeline) | 3–4 | Tenders ingested; AI agents callable |
| **Phase 3: Core Product** ← **Demo milestone** | E06 (Opportunity Discovery), E07 (Proposal Generation) | 5–8 | End-to-end: discover → analyse → draft → export |
| **Phase 4: Commercial** ← **Beta milestone** | E08 (Billing), E09 (Notifications & Calendar) | 9–10 | Paid subscriptions live; alerts and calendar sync working |
| **Phase 5: Scale & Launch** ← **MVP milestone** | E10 (Collaboration), E11 (Grants), E12 (Analytics & Admin) | 11–14 | Full feature set; admin platform; analytics dashboards |

